    "synopsis": "Five years after House Chimaeros fell to heresy, Luk Kar Chimaeros has cast aside his name to become the Knight of Ashes, a Freeblade hunting his treacherous step-mother Alicia Kar Manticos across the stars with a band of fellow exiles. Just as the chase nears its end, catastrophe descends on his homeworld of Adrastapol — a massive ork invasion that threatens the surviving noble Houses, leaving High King Danial Tan Draconis to unite them or watch his world burn. Luk faces an agonising choice: press on with his quest for justice and honour, or return home to fight beside his former brothers and risk being branded a heretic forever.",
